Description: A 20-something bachelor bartender becomes an unlikely parent when an ex-girlfriend leaves a baby girl on his doorstep.

Title: Modern Love: Mumbai
Description: Exploring 6 unique yet universal stories of human connection and love in its varied forms – romantic, platonic, parental, sexual, familial, marital, self love.

Title: Skam
Description: The story of young teenagers and pupils on Hartvig Nissens upper secondary school in Oslo, and their troubles, scandals and everyday life. Each season is told from a different person's point of view.

Title: Wolf Like Me
Description: Gary is an emotional wreck and struggles to provide for his daughter since the death of his wife. Mary has a secret she can't bring herself to share with anyone. The universe brought these two together for a reason.

Title: Gavin & Stacey
Description: Gavin and Stacey have been continuing their romance on-line and by telephone for the last six months. Now they want to be together but will their friends and family let them?

Title: Muhtesem Yüzyil
Description: From 1520, follows Suleiman the Magnificent and his relatives from his great conquests to the "Battle of Szigeth".

Title: The Finder
Description: An Iraq war vet suffers a brain injury that triggers the ability to see connections between seemingly unrelated events, objects or people.

Title: Al Hayba
Description: In a village by the Lebanon-Syria border, the head of an arms-smuggling clan contends with family conflicts, power struggles and complicated love.

Title: The Pillars of the Earth
Description: Set against a backdrop of war, religious strife and power struggles which tears lives and families apart.

Title: Young & Hungry
Description: A well-off young tech entrepreneur hires a feisty young food blogger to be his personal chef.

Title: Bob Hearts Abishola
Description: An American guy falls in love with his Nigerian nurse.

Title: Picket Fences
Description: An aging Sheriff tries to keep the peace in Rome, Wisconsin, a small town plagued by bizarre and violent crimes.

Title: The Avengers
Description: A quirky spy show of the adventures of eccentrically suave British Agent John Steed and his predominately female partners.

Title: Moonlighting
Description: The quirky cases of a former model and a smart aleck detective who manage a private detective agency.
